name: Queen of the Fairies Flora Crown
description:
For the ultimate spring fairy queens, put on your crown and spread some fairy dust!

This flora crown adds a little kawaii to any outfit, wedding, engagement, party or frog prince!

Made from silk flowers that look exceptionally lifelike, you'll look like you have real flowers on your head 

Each crown is put together with human hands in Fremantle, Western Australia, by the fairy queens at Esther Jane Fox
